extends ../layout
block content
  .logo-div
    img.logo-image(src='/public/image/logo.png')
  .agree-title
    h2 oauth 서버 로그인 서비스 동의

  .agree-listBox
    ul  
      each items in reqInfo
        li= items 
    p 위의 표기된 정보를 resourceServer에서 받아옵니다. 동의하십니까?
  .agree-buttonBox
    form(action=`/oauth/callback/`, method='post') 
      input(type='hidden',name='client_id' ,value=client_id)
      input(type='hidden',name='redirect_uri' ,value=redirect_uri)
      input(type='hidden',name='state' ,value=state)
      input(type='hidden',name='manager' ,value=1)
      input(type='hidden',name='reqInfo' ,value=reqInfo)
      button.agreeButton(type='submit') 동의함
    
    button.noAgreeButton(type='button') 동의안함


  block contents